<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/index.css" />

    <title>Setak D'gaja</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('nav.html') %>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section_introduce">
        <div class="copy1">
          세탁을 자유롭게! <br />
          세탁드가자에 맡겨보세요
        </div>
        <div class="copy2">
          힘들었던 세탁, 이제 주문 한번으로 해결할 수 있어요
        </div>
        <div class="copy3">오늘 주문하면 내일 완료되어요</div>

        <a href="/orderPost"><button id="order-button">주문하러가기</button></a>
      </div>

      <div class="section_banner">
        <!-- <img src={`http://localhost:1004/image/laudryfree.jpg`}> -->
        <!-- <img src="http://localhost:1004/image/laundryfree.jpg" > -->
        <!-- <img class="banner" src="http://localhost:3000/image/laundryfree.jpg" > -->
        <img
          src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/closeup-gray-sofa-with-basket-folded-clothes-small-table-near-it_181624-36936.jpg?w=1380&t=st=1672809874~exp=1672810474~hmac=707a7082718d6accc317b517bbcee52f41616d1e5400712c598dd52247203f71"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

  <style>



    .section {
      display: flex;
    }

    .section_introduce {
      /* flex-grow: 4; */
      width: 40%;
      margin-top: 200px;
      margin-left: 60px;
    }

    .copy1 {
      font-size: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .section_banner {
      /* flex-grow: 6; */
      width: 60%;
    }

    .copy2 {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .copy3 {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .banner {
      width: 100%;
      height: 50%;
    }

    #order-button {
      /* Add some padding and a font size */
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 18px;

      /* Add a background color and some text styling */
      background-color: white;
      color: #312f1f;
      font-weight: bold;

      /* Add a border and border radius */
      border: 2px solid #312f1f;
      border-radius: 10px;

      /* Add a hover effect */
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    #order-button:hover {
      background-color: #312f1f;
      color: white;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1600px) {
      .section {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .section_introduce {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-left: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .section_banner {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</html>
